'''Sixx:A.M.'''是一支2007年由[[Nikki_Sixx|Nikki Sixx]]、[[DJ_Ashba|DJ Ashba]]與[[James_Michael|James Michael]]成立於[[美國|美國]][[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]的[[硬式搖滾|硬式搖滾]]樂團，樂團名稱來自三位創團成員的姓氏組合。該樂團最有名的兩首歌為{{tsl|en|Life Is Beautiful (Sixx:A.M. song)}}和[[Lies_of_the_Beautiful_People|Lies of the Beautiful People]]。至目前為止該樂團已發行5張[[錄音室專輯|錄音室專輯]]:[[The_Heroin_Diaries_Soundtrack|The Heroin Diaries Soundtrack]] (2007)、[[This_Is_Gonna_Hurt|This Is Gonna Hurt]] (2011)、[[Modern_Vintage|Modern Vintage]] (2014)、[[Prayers_for_the_Damned|Prayers for the Damned]]、{{tsl|en|Prayers for the Blessed}} (2016)與3張[[迷你專輯|迷你專輯]]: [[X-Mas_In_Hell|X-Mas In Hell]] (2008); [[Live_Is_Beautiful|Live Is Beautiful]] (2008)、{{tsl|en|7 (Sixx:A.M. EP)|7 (專輯)}} (2011)。

